---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Careers"
  description="Engineering roles and opportunities at RePass Cloud Pty Ltd. We hire engineers who build real things — people who take ownership, communicate clearly, and care about quality."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">
        <i class="bi bi-briefcase"></i>
        Join the team
      </div>
      <h1>Work with RePass Cloud.</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">
        We hire engineers and collaborators who build real things — people who take ownership,
        communicate clearly, and care about the quality of what they ship.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
          Get in touch <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About working here -->
  <section class="section bg-surface">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="showcase-split" style="align-items:start;">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">What we're about</div>
          <h2>Engineering-led. Remote-friendly.</h2>
          <p style="color:var(--rpc-muted); line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:1rem;">
            RePass Cloud is a software engineering consultancy focused on solving complex technical
            problems through code. Our engineers design and build automation systems, backend
            platforms, infrastructure tooling, and integrations for organisations that need reliable
            technical solutions.
          </p>
          <p style="color:var(--rpc-muted); line-height:1.8;">
            We are a hybrid, digital-first team. Some of us are fully remote. Some work from offices
            nowhere near our Sydney head office. What we care about is output, not where you sit.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">What we value</div>
          <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1rem; margin-top:0.5rem;">
            <div style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem;">
              <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill" style="color:var(--rpc-valid); flex-shrink:0; margin-top:0.15rem;"></i>
              <div>
                <div style="font-weight:600; margin-bottom:0.2rem;">Build real things</div>
                <div style="font-size:0.875rem; color:var(--rpc-muted);">We work on production systems that organisations depend on daily.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem;">
              <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill" style="color:var(--rpc-valid); flex-shrink:0; margin-top:0.15rem;"></i>
              <div>
                <div style="font-weight:600; margin-bottom:0.2rem;">Own your work</div>
                <div style="font-size:0.875rem; color:var(--rpc-muted);">Engineers own their areas end-to-end. No approval chains for obvious improvements.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem;">
              <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill" style="color:var(--rpc-valid); flex-shrink:0; margin-top:0.15rem;"></i>
              <div>
                <div style="font-weight:600; margin-bottom:0.2rem;">Quality matters</div>
                <div style="font-size:0.875rem; color:var(--rpc-muted);">We build for production, not for demos. Security and reliability are non-negotiable.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem;">
              <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill" style="color:var(--rpc-valid); flex-shrink:0; margin-top:0.15rem;"></i>
              <div>
                <div style="font-weight:600; margin-bottom:0.2rem;">Output over optics</div>
                <div style="font-size:0.875rem; color:var(--rpc-muted);">Remote and async-friendly. We judge on results, not visibility.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Open roles -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px;">
      <div class="section-label">Open roles</div>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Current opportunities</h2>

      <div class="aethon-card" style="background:var(--rpc-bg); border:1px solid var(--rpc-border); border-left: 4px solid var(--rpc-primary);">
        <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.75rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">
          <i class="bi bi-person-workspace" style="font-size:1.5rem; color:var(--rpc-text-strong);"></i>
          <div style="font-weight:700; font-size:1.1rem;">Open application</div>
        </div>
        <p style="color:var(--rpc-muted); line-height:1.75; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
          We don't always post open roles publicly. If you are a strong engineer interested in
          enterprise software, cloud automation, identity systems, or developer tooling — get in
          touch. Tell us what you build and why you're interested.
        </p>
        <div class="tech-stack" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          <span class="badge badge-secondary">.NET</span>
          <span class="badge badge-primary">Azure / AWS</span>
          <span class="badge badge-secondary">PowerShell</span>
          <span class="badge badge-secondary">Identity</span>
          <span class="badge badge-secondary">Infrastructure</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">
          Send us a message <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Culture cards -->
  <section class="section bg-surface">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
        <div class="section-label">Culture</div>
        <h2>How we work</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="principle-card">
          <div class="principle-icon"><i class="bi bi-globe2"></i></div>
          <div class="principle-title">Remote-first</div>
          <div class="principle-desc">We are distributed by default. Collaboration tools, async communication, and strong documentation are how we operate.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="principle-card">
          <div class="principle-icon"><i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i></div>
          <div class="principle-title">Engineering career paths</div>
          <div class="principle-desc">We support engineers who want to go deep technically. Management is not the only path forward here.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="principle-card">
          <div class="principle-icon"><i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i></div>
          <div class="principle-title">Security-minded team</div>
          <div class="principle-desc">Every team member thinks about security as part of their normal work, not as a separate checklist.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Hiring info links -->
  <section class="section-sm">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px;">
      <div class="section-label">Explore</div>
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">More about working here</h3>
      <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.5rem;">
        <a href="/careers/jobs/" style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.75rem; color:var(--rpc-text); text-decoration:none; padding:0.875rem 1rem; background:var(--rpc-surface); border:1px solid var(--rpc-border); border-radius:var(--radius-3);">
          <i class="bi bi-briefcase" style="color:var(--rpc-muted);"></i>
          <span>Open roles</span>
          <i class="bi bi-arrow-right" style="margin-left:auto; color:var(--rpc-muted);"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="/careers/how-we-hire/" style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.75rem; color:var(--rpc-text); text-decoration:none; padding:0.875rem 1rem; background:var(--rpc-surface); border:1px solid var(--rpc-border); border-radius:var(--radius-3);">
          <i class="bi bi-people" style="color:var(--rpc-muted);"></i>
          <span>How we hire — our end-to-end process, from application to offer</span>
          <i class="bi bi-arrow-right" style="margin-left:auto; color:var(--rpc-muted);"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="/careers/culture/" style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.75rem; color:var(--rpc-text); text-decoration:none; padding:0.875rem 1rem; background:var(--rpc-surface); border:1px solid var(--rpc-border); border-radius:var(--radius-3);">
          <i class="bi bi-heart" style="color:var(--rpc-muted);"></i>
          <span>Culture & Belonging — how we work and what we value</span>
          <i class="bi bi-arrow-right" style="margin-left:auto; color:var(--rpc-muted);"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="/careers/candidate-guide/" style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.75rem; color:var(--rpc-text); text-decoration:none; padding:0.875rem 1rem; background:var(--rpc-surface); border:1px solid var(--rpc-border); border-radius:var(--radius-3);">
          <i class="bi bi-journal-text" style="color:var(--rpc-muted);"></i>
          <span>Candidate Preparation Guide — what to expect and how to prepare</span>
          <i class="bi bi-arrow-right" style="margin-left:auto; color:var(--rpc-muted);"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="/careers/equal-opportunity/" style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.75rem; color:var(--rpc-text); text-decoration:none; padding:0.875rem 1rem; background:var(--rpc-surface); border:1px solid var(--rpc-border); border-radius:var(--radius-3);">
          <i class="bi bi-balance" style="color:var(--rpc-muted);"></i>
          <span>Equal Opportunity Statement</span>
          <i class="bi bi-arrow-right" style="margin-left:auto; color:var(--rpc-muted);"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="/careers/applicant-privacy-notice/" style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.75rem; color:var(--rpc-text); text-decoration:none; padding:0.875rem 1rem; background:var(--rpc-surface); border:1px solid var(--rpc-border); border-radius:var(--radius-3);">
          <i class="bi bi-shield-check" style="color:var(--rpc-muted);"></i>
          <span>Applicant Privacy Notice — how we handle your data</span>
          <i class="bi bi-arrow-right" style="margin-left:auto; color:var(--rpc-muted);"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.75rem; color:var(--rpc-text); text-decoration:none; padding:0.875rem 1rem; background:var(--rpc-surface); border:1px solid var(--rpc-border); border-radius:var(--radius-3);">
          <i class="bi bi-envelope" style="color:var(--rpc-muted);"></i>
          <span>Contact us with your background and what you're looking for</span>
          <i class="bi bi-arrow-right" style="margin-left:auto; color:var(--rpc-muted);"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
